 their vital contributions to ecosystem functioning in fragmented tropical landscapes.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Farneda, F\u00e1bio Z.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rocha, Ricardo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "L\u00f3pez-Baucells, Adri\u00e0", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sampaio, Erica M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Palmeirim, Jorge M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Bobrowiec, Paulo E.D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Grelle, Carlos E.V.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Meyer, Christoph F.J.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8d5110db592c8abb1be4f778cb0e525f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/697df2fbb5cad9e37d29854a45fd8ad605601718c24d1e933bd81852c953be9d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/4P4C3BXY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/4P4C3BXY", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/7cfa7c86440c0f486392c473fc6f3f53!/b312025-314492", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"pages": "192-199", "title": "Biological Conservation", "volume": "218"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/8d5110db592c8abb1be4f778cb0e525f"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:4P4C3BXY"}, {"